{"prompt": "Design a professional site for a wealth management firm. The color scheme should feature a refined yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Wealth Management</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #e6c300; /* Refined yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #c0a300 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        #branding {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-bottom: #e6c300 2px solid;\n        }\n        #branding h2 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: #e6c300;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h3 {\n            color: #e6c300;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #services, #about {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .service-item, .about-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-item h4, .about-item h4 {\n            color: #c0a300;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #e6c300;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            color: #c0a300;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Wealth Management</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n    <section id=\"branding\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Partner in Financial Growth</h2>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div id=\"about\">\n                <h3>About Us</h3>\n                <div class=\"about-item\">\n                    <p>Apex Wealth Management is dedicated to providing personalized financial strategies that align with your unique goals. We believe in transparency, integrity, and a client-centric approach to help you navigate the complexities of wealth building and preservation.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"services\">\n                <h3>Our Services</h3>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Investment Planning</h4>\n                    <p>Crafting diversified portfolios tailored to your risk tolerance and objectives.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Retirement Planning</h4>\n                    <p>Securing your financial future with comprehensive retirement strategies.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Estate Planning</h4>\n                    <p>Ensuring your legacy is protected and passed on according to your wishes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Risk Management</h4>\n                    <p>Identifying and mitigating potential financial risks.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"contact\">\n                <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n                <p>Ready to take the next step? Reach out to us for a confidential consultation.</p>\n                <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@apexwealth.com\">info@apexwealth.com</a></p>\n                <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Wealth Management. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}